content:
Required editions: Lightning Experience, Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

Setup Considerations:

* Flows created from the Customer Contact Requests page in Setup don’t appear in the list of flows on the Flows page.
* Use guided setup experience on the Customer Contact Requests page in Setup for contact request flows.
* If you customize Reason picklist values after flow creation, manually update picklist values in Flow Builder.
* Contact request flows don’t support pause actions on flow screens.
* To use a contact request flow from an AppExchange package, update contact request owner to user in your org.

Agent Considerations:

* All Standard User and System Administrator profiles have access to the object by default. Ensure agents' profiles have at least read access on the contact request object.
* When relating a contact request to a new record, populate relevant fields with information from the contact request.
title: Service Cloud Contact Request Considerations
